trans-unit.source: This method compares the parameters `Source` and `Pattern` and returns the same results as the [Like Operator](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden sammenligner parameterne `Source` og `Pattern` og returnerer de samme resultatene som den [Like-operatoren](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The result is a Boolean value indicating whether or not the string satisfies the pattern.
trans-unit.target: Resultatet er en boolsk verdi som angir om strengen oppfyller mønsteret.

trans-unit.source: Required.

trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_String" name="String" href=""> </xref> Uttrykket overensstemmelse samsvarer med mønsteret-konvensjoner som beskrevet i Like-operatoren.

trans-unit.source: Specifies how to compare strings to patterns, according to the <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.CompareMethod"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Angir hvordan strenger til mønstrene sammenlignes i henhold til den <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.CompareMethod"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Can be <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbBinaryCompare" name="vbBinaryCompare" href=""></xref> for binary comparison or <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbTextCompare" name="vbTextCompare" href=""></xref> for comparison based on a case-insensitive text sort order determined by your system's <xref uid="langword_csharp_LocaleID" name="LocaleID" href=""></xref> value.
trans-unit.target: Kan være <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbBinaryCompare" name="vbBinaryCompare" href=""> </xref> for binært eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbTextCompare" name="vbTextCompare" href=""> </xref> for sammenligning basert på en samlingstype teksten sorteringsrekkefølge henhold systemets <xref uid="langword_csharp_LocaleID" name="LocaleID" href=""> </xref> verdi.

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_Boolean" name="Boolean" href=""></xref> value indicating whether or not the string satisfies the pattern.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_Boolean" name="Boolean" href=""> </xref> verdi som angir hvorvidt strengen oppfyller mønsteret.

trans-unit.source: If the value in string satisfies the pattern contained in pattern, result is <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis verdien i strengen oppfyller mønsteret i mønsteret, <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: If the string does not satisfy the pattern, result is <xref uid="langword_csharp_False" name="False" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis strengen ikke oppfyller mønsteret, <xref uid="langword_csharp_False" name="False" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: If both string and pattern are empty strings, the result is <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis både streng og mønsteret tomme strenger, resultatet er <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Compares the parameters Source and Pattern and returns the same results as the operator, using binary comparison.
trans-unit.target: Sammenligner parameterne Source og Pattern og returnerer de samme resultatene som den operator, med binært.

trans-unit.source: This method compares the parameters `Source` and `Pattern` and returns the same results as the [Like Operator](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The result is a Boolean value indicating whether or not the string satisfies the pattern.
trans-unit.target: Resultatet er en boolsk verdi som angir om strengen oppfyller mønsteret.

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_Boolean" name="Boolean" href=""></xref> value indicating whether or not the string satisfies the pattern.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_Boolean" name="Boolean" href=""> </xref> verdi som angir hvorvidt strengen oppfyller mønsteret.

trans-unit.source: If the value in string satisfies the pattern contained in pattern, result is <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis verdien i strengen oppfyller mønsteret i mønsteret, <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: If the string does not satisfy the pattern, result is <xref uid="langword_csharp_False" name="False" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis strengen ikke oppfyller mønsteret, <xref uid="langword_csharp_False" name="False" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: If both string and pattern are empty strings, the result is <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis både streng og mønsteret tomme strenger, resultatet er <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Compares the parameters Source and Pattern and returns the same results as the operator, using text comparison.
trans-unit.target: Sammenligner parameterne Source og Pattern og returnerer de samme resultatene som den operatoren, ved hjelp av tekst sammenligningen.

trans-unit.source: This method compares the parameters `Source` and `Pattern` and returns the same results as the [Like Operator](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden sammenligner parameterne `Source` og `Pattern` og returnerer de samme resultatene som den [Like-operatoren](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The result is a `Boolean` value indicating whether or not the string satisfies the pattern.
trans-unit.target: Resultatet er en `Boolean` verdi som angir hvorvidt strengen oppfyller mønsteret.

trans-unit.source: This method is similar to <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.CompilerServices.StringType.StrLike%2A> except that it always performs a comparison based on a case-insensitive text sort order determined by your system's `LocaleID` value.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden er lik <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.CompilerServices.StringType.StrLike%2A>bortsett fra at det alltid utfører en sammenligning basert på en samlingstype teksten sorteringsrekkefølge henhold systemets `LocaleID` verdi.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.CompilerServices.StringType.StrLike%2A>
